The paper discusses the development of spiking neural networks for object recognition, which falls under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the use of temporal coding schemes and data augmentation techniques suggests a focus on system and control theory (cs.SY).
